snippet.title: Frankenstein Walkthrough, ZX Spectrum
snippet.description:
A walkthrough of the ZX Spectrum game, Frankenstein. A 1987 text adventure from CRL. The number at the top-right corresponds with the location number on the map at https://maps.speccy.cz/map.php?id=Frankenstein . From the recording originally sent by Hippy Smith to http://www.rzxarchive.co.uk/ .

#ZXSpectrum #RetroGaming #Walkthrough
